{"ID":822,"post_content":"[vc_row type=\"full_width_background\" full_screen_row_position=\"middle\" column_margin=\"default\" bg_color=\"#0a0a0a\" scene_position=\"center\" top_padding=\"4%\" bottom_padding=\"6%\" text_color=\"dark\" text_align=\"left\" row_border_radius=\"none\" row_border_radius_applies=\"bg\" overlay_strength=\"0.3\" gradient_direction=\"left_to_right\" shape_divider_position=\"bottom\" bg_image_animation=\"none\"][vc_column column_padding=\"padding-3-percent\" column_padding_position=\"all\" background_color_opacity=\"1\" column_shadow=\"none\" column_border_radius=\"none\" column_link_target=\"_self\" width=\"1\/1\" tablet_width_inherit=\"default\"][vc_column_text]\n<div style=\"max-width:860px; margin:0 auto; font-family:Georgia, serif; color:#1a1a1a;\">\n\n<div style=\"background:#e8e8e6; color:#1a1a1a; padding:2.5em 2.5em 2em; border-radius:8px; margin-bottom:2.5em;\">\n  <p style=\"text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:0.15em; font-size:0.75em; color:#c8a96e; margin:0 0 0.5em; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">Collective Intelligence<\/p>\n  <h1 style=\"color:#fff; font-size:2em; margin:0 0 0.4em; line-height:1.2;\">SEO Audit &amp; Progress Report<\/h1>\n  <p style=\"color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6); margin:0; font-size:0.95em; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">sulibreaks.com &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; May 2026<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- Summary bar -->\n<div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:1em; margin-bottom:2.5em;\">\n  <div style=\"background:#f0faf0; border:1px solid #b6e0b6; border-radius:8px; padding:1.2em 1.5em; text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:2em; font-weight:700; color:#2e7d32; margin:0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">11<\/p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:0.8em; color:#555; margin:0.3em 0 0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">Issues Fixed<\/p>\n  <\/div>\n  <div style=\"background:#fff8e8; border:1px solid #f0d080; border-radius:8px; padding:1.2em 1.5em; text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:2em; font-weight:700; color:#b8860b; margin:0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">8<\/p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:0.8em; color:#555; margin:0.3em 0 0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">Pages Optimised<\/p>\n  <\/div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5ff; border:1px solid #c5c5e8; border-radius:8px; padding:1.2em 1.5em; text-align:center;\">\n    <p style=\"font-size:2em; font-weight:700; color:#3949ab; margin:0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">Phase 1<\/p>\n    <p style=\"font-size:0.8em; color:#555; margin:0.3em 0 0; font-family:Arial,sans-serif;\">Complete<\/p>\n  <\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- Issues Found -->\n<h2 style=\"font-size:1.3em; border-bottom:2px solid #1a1a1a; padding-bottom:0.4em; margin-bottom:1.2em;\">What the Audit Found<\/h2>\n\n<table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.9em; margin-bottom:2.5em;\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr style=\"background:#e8e8e6; color:#1a1a1a;\">\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:left; font-weight:600;\">#<\/th>\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:left; font-weight:600;\">Issue<\/th>\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:left; font-weight:600;\">Impact<\/th>\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:left; font-weight:600;\">Status<\/th>\n    <\/tr>\n  <\/thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fff;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">1<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">Page titles missing or generic on all key pages<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">High<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; color:#2e7d32; font-weight:600;\">\u2713 Fixed<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">2<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">Meta descriptions missing on all key pages<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">High<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; color:#2e7d32; font-weight:600;\">\u2713 Fixed<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fff;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">3<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">Speaker page: no H1, ~165 words, no client names, no testimonials, no FAQs<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">High<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; color:#2e7d32; font-weight:600;\">\u2713 Fixed<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">4<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\"><code style=\"background:#f0f0f0; padding:0.1em 0.4em; border-radius:3px;\">user-scalable=0<\/code> in viewport tag (accessibility &amp; SEO issue)<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">Medium<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; color:#2e7d32; font-weight:600;\">\u2713 Fixed<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fff;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">5<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">3 broken event ticket links on homepage (LA, Birmingham, Beckenham) \u2014 all returning 404<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">Medium<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; color:#2e7d32; font-weight:600;\">\u2713 Fixed<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">6<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">No service sub-pages \u2014 \"Services\" had no depth for Google to index<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">High<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; color:#2e7d32; font-weight:600;\">\u2713 Fixed<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fff;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">7<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">Services page had no internal links to service detail pages<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee;\">Medium<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; color:#2e7d32; font-weight:600;\">\u2713 Fixed<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n  <\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n\n<!-- What we fixed -->\n<h2 style=\"font-size:1.3em; border-bottom:2px solid #1a1a1a; padding-bottom:0.4em; margin-bottom:1.2em;\">What Was Fixed \u2014 Phase 1<\/h2>\n\n<div style=\"margin-bottom:2.5em;\">\n\n  <div style=\"border-left:4px solid #c8a96e; padding:0.8em 1.2em; margin-bottom:0.8em; background:#fffdf7; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.9em;\">\n    <strong>Page Titles &amp; Meta Descriptions<\/strong><br>\n    <span style=\"color:#555;\">Rewrote titles and meta descriptions for Homepage, Speaker, Services, and Book Me. Each title is now keyword-targeted and includes Suli's name. Meta descriptions are commercial and click-focused.<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"border-left:4px solid #c8a96e; padding:0.8em 1.2em; margin-bottom:0.8em; background:#fffdf7; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.9em;\">\n    <strong>Speaker Page \u2014 Full Rebuild<\/strong><br>\n    <span style=\"color:#555;\">Added H1 (\"Suli Breaks \u2013 Motivational Speaker &amp; Spoken Word Artist\"), expanded from ~165 to 700+ words, named 10+ major clients in body text (BT, LinkedIn, Lloyds Banking Group, Microsoft, Meta, Nike, BBC, Houses of Parliament, TED, UN), added 4 real client testimonials, and 5 FAQs covering format, duration, virtual events, international availability, and how to book.<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"border-left:4px solid #c8a96e; padding:0.8em 1.2em; margin-bottom:0.8em; background:#fffdf7; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.9em;\">\n    <strong>Viewport Tag Fix<\/strong><br>\n    <span style=\"color:#555;\">Removed <code style=\"background:#f0f0f0; padding:0.1em 0.3em; border-radius:3px;\">user-scalable=0<\/code> from the theme's viewport meta tag. This was preventing mobile users from zooming and flagged as both an accessibility failure and a negative mobile-usability signal.<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"border-left:4px solid #c8a96e; padding:0.8em 1.2em; margin-bottom:0.8em; background:#fffdf7; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.9em;\">\n    <strong>Broken Event Links Removed<\/strong><br>\n    <span style=\"color:#555;\">Removed 3 broken ticket links from the homepage events section: LA show (November 15th \u2014 Eventbrite 404), Birmingham show (Hockley Social Club \u2014 Eventbrite 404), and Beckenham entry (linked to wrong event URL). 3 valid event links remain.<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"border-left:4px solid #c8a96e; padding:0.8em 1.2em; margin-bottom:0.8em; background:#fffdf7; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.9em;\">\n    <strong>4 Service Sub-Pages Created<\/strong><br>\n    <span style=\"color:#555;\">Created <a href=\"\/services\/keynote-speaking\/\" style=\"color:#c8a96e;\">\/services\/keynote-speaking<\/a>, <a href=\"\/services\/workshops\/\" style=\"color:#c8a96e;\">\/services\/workshops<\/a>, <a href=\"\/services\/live-performances\/\" style=\"color:#c8a96e;\">\/services\/live-performances<\/a>, and <a href=\"\/services\/brand-collaborations\/\" style=\"color:#c8a96e;\">\/services\/brand-collaborations<\/a>. Each has a keyword-targeted H1, 600\u2013800 words of original content, 4 FAQs, and a CTA. Services parent page now links to all four.<\/span>\n  <\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<!-- Page status table -->\n<h2 style=\"font-size:1.3em; border-bottom:2px solid #1a1a1a; padding-bottom:0.4em; margin-bottom:1.2em;\">Current Page SEO Status<\/h2>\n\n<table style=\"width:100%; border-collapse:collapse; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.85em; margin-bottom:2.5em;\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr style=\"background:#e8e8e6; color:#1a1a1a;\">\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:left;\">Page<\/th>\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:center;\">Title<\/th>\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:center;\">Meta<\/th>\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:center;\">H1<\/th>\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:center;\">Content<\/th>\n      <th style=\"padding:0.7em 1em; text-align:center;\">FAQs<\/th>\n    <\/tr>\n  <\/thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fff;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-weight:600;\">Homepage<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-weight:600;\">Speaker<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 700+ words<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 5<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fff;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-weight:600;\">Services<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-weight:600;\">Book Me<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#888;\">\u2014<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fff;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-weight:600;\">Keynote Speaking <span style=\"background:#e8f5e9; color:#2e7d32; font-size:0.75em; padding:0.1em 0.5em; border-radius:3px; font-weight:400;\">new<\/span><\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 700+ words<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 4<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-weight:600;\">Workshops <span style=\"background:#e8f5e9; color:#2e7d32; font-size:0.75em; padding:0.1em 0.5em; border-radius:3px; font-weight:400;\">new<\/span><\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 700+ words<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 4<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fff;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-weight:600;\">Live Performances <span style=\"background:#e8f5e9; color:#2e7d32; font-size:0.75em; padding:0.1em 0.5em; border-radius:3px; font-weight:400;\">new<\/span><\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 700+ words<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 4<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n    <tr style=\"background:#fafafa;\">\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; font-weight:600;\">Brand Collaborations <span style=\"background:#e8f5e9; color:#2e7d32; font-size:0.75em; padding:0.1em 0.5em; border-radius:3px; font-weight:400;\">new<\/span><\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 700+ words<\/td>\n      <td style=\"padding:0.65em 1em; border-bottom:1px solid #eee; text-align:center; color:#2e7d32;\">\u2713 4<\/td>\n    <\/tr>\n  <\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n\n<!-- Phase 2 & 3 -->\n<h2 style=\"font-size:1.3em; border-bottom:2px solid #1a1a1a; padding-bottom:0.4em; margin-bottom:1.2em;\">What's Coming Next<\/h2>\n\n<div style=\"display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:1.5em; margin-bottom:2.5em; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.9em;\">\n\n  <div style=\"background:#fff8e8; border:1px solid #f0d080; border-radius:8px; padding:1.5em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight:700; margin:0 0 0.8em; color:#b8860b; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:0.8em; letter-spacing:0.1em;\">Phase 2 \u2014 Conversion &amp; Authority<\/p>\n    <ul style=\"margin:0; padding-left:1.2em; line-height:1.9; color:#444;\">\n      <li>Reorder homepage sections \u2014 social proof higher<\/li>\n      <li>Rename \"Book Me\" for clearer intent<\/li>\n      <li>Add FAQ sections to remaining key pages<\/li>\n      <li>Improve enquiry flow and response signals<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n  <\/div>\n\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5ff; border:1px solid #c5c5e8; border-radius:8px; padding:1.5em;\">\n    <p style=\"font-weight:700; margin:0 0 0.8em; color:#3949ab; text-transform:uppercase; font-size:0.8em; letter-spacing:0.1em;\">Phase 3 \u2014 AI Search &amp; Long-Term<\/p>\n    <ul style=\"margin:0; padding-left:1.2em; line-height:1.9; color:#444;\">\n      <li>Person + Event + FAQ schema markup (JSON-LD)<\/li>\n      <li>Blog \/ Insights section<\/li>\n      <li>E-E-A-T signals \u2014 press, awards, media logos<\/li>\n      <li>Image compression + Core Web Vitals<\/li>\n    <\/ul>\n  <\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n\n<div style=\"background:#1a1a1a; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5); padding:1.2em 1.5em; border-radius:6px; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:0.8em; text-align:center;\">\n  Prepared by Collective Intelligence &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; mail@chrisbradshaw.ai &nbsp;\u00b7&nbsp; May 2026\n<\/div>\n\n<\/div>\n[\/vc_column_text][\/vc_column][\/vc_row]","post_title":"SEO Report \u2014 May 2026","post_name":"seo-report","post_modified":"2026-05-31 15:15:14"}
